    </a>
    </td>
    
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    Radius Stun spell which stuns all targets within your immediate area. Target's stun time amount depends on the caster's skill and level. If the target is hit by melee combat the spell is negated.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>General<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Area effect Stun
    </font>
    
    </td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">
    
